[recent-changes]
- 2026-07-07: Naming-mandate migration — `.machine_readable/6a2/` renamed to `.machine_readable/descriptiles/` and `.machine_readable/agent_instructions/` to `.machine_readable/bot_directives/` per the estate canon (standards/CANONICAL-NAMES.adoc; the 6a2 name is fully deprecated). All in-repo path references updated (README, EXPLAINME, ECOSYSTEM-STATUS, 0-AI-MANIFEST, .claude/CLAUDE.md, wiki/*, gitmerge-paralleliser classifier test); docs/governance/CRG-AUDIT-2026-04-18.adoc deliberately left untouched as a dated historical record. Fresh full-suite baseline 113/113 recorded above. Same-day PR series also adds: megasweep README + templates/settings detectors (#180), and the QoL daily loop (just estate-refresh / estate / install + web HUD auto-load of export.json).
- 2026-06-26: Consolidation COMPLETED + governance/CI hardening — the deferrals listed in the 2026-06-21 entry below are now resolved. (1) Extraction/de-vendoring: the five former local-only standalones (bitfuckit, contractiles, recon-silly-ation, scaffoldia, stateful-artefacts) now have real GitHub forge repos and are wired in as gitlinks; rpa-elysium was de-vendored from its 171-file tree to a real gitlink (bda6720), and total-recall (the byte-identical total-upgrade duplicate) was dropped. The displaced vendored content is PRESERVED on two pushed archive branches: archive/rpa-elysium-vendored-2026-06-21 and archive/vendored-standalones-2026-06-21. .gitmodules now declares EIGHT consistent gitlink submodules (git-scripts, git-reticulator, rpa-elysium, bitfuckit, contractiles, recon-silly-ation, scaffoldia, stateful-artefacts) — every declaration maps to a 160000 gitlink, none broken or drifted. Still embedded as ordinary trees BY DESIGN: total-upgrade (RSR scaffold) and git-morph/git-seo. (2) hypatia neurosymbolic findings reduced 222->71 across the session — via the extraction (drops vendored-tree noise) + real first-party source fixes (#160: src/commands/apply.rs error-handling, src/verisimdb.rs blocking-client build) + workflow timeout-minutes hardening (#162). Residual 71 is dominated by epic-#93 ReScript->AffineScript migration debt and known false positives (web/app.js SVG xmlns, clippy::pedantic style). (3) Governance/CI: standards reusable pins refreshed + retired scorecard-enforcer dropped; licence normalised to the canonical MPL-2.0 + CC-BY-SA-4.0 pair (#157); estate-wide standards-treadmill breakage fixed — rust-ci `toolchain` input + LICENSE SPDX header (#161); CLADE [status] lifecycle block backfilled (#156); dormant push-email notification workflow added (#158); Nix flake removed, Guix-only (#144); megasweep parallel estate-sweep runner added (#137); security dependency updates (#159). Merged across the #130–#162 PR series. Docs synced this session: this file, ECOSYSTEM-STATUS.adoc, ECOSYSTEM-MAP.adoc, CHANGELOG.md, docs/PHASE-2-STANDALONE-VS-LOCAL-VERIFICATION-2026-06-02.adoc, config/tools.ncl, README.adoc, NEUROSYM.a2ml. NOTE: the older dated entries below are retained as historical record — where they say "5 local-only standalones", "two consistent gitlinks", or "rpa-elysium gitlink broken", read them as superseded by this entry.
- 2026-06-21: Consolidation — .gitmodules reconciled to ground truth. Pruned the three stale submodule declarations whose paths are committed as ordinary trees, not gitlinks, keeping all content: rpa-elysium (171-file vendored tree — its GitHub forge exists and is reachable but has DIVERGED from the vendored snapshot: of 155 common files 141 differ, with 16 vendored-only + 23 forge-only files, so de-vendoring is a separate human-gated merge, not done here), total-upgrade + total-recall (28-file RSR scaffolds sharing tree 84d1361 = byte-identical duplicates; their GitLab repos are unverifiable from this environment). .gitmodules now declares exactly the two consistent gitlinks (git-scripts, git-reticulator); git submodule status/update no longer choke. The orphan-gitlink half of this surgery (avatar-fabrication-facility, claim-forge) already shipped in f0586e8 (PR #130, "give ClusterFuzzLite a Dockerfile and drop orphan gitlinks"). Deferred: rpa-elysium<->forge reconciliation, extracting the 5 local-only standalones to forge repos, de-duping total-upgrade/total-recall. Doc: docs/PHASE-2-STANDALONE-VS-LOCAL-VERIFICATION-2026-06-02.adoc updated (new "Reconciliation executed" section).
- 2026-06-20: Estate-representation foundation (representation -> visualisation). The Rust `types` module is now the single schema of record: added Estate (multi-estate parameterisation; hyperpolymath = estate #1), ExternalSeam + SeamDomain (loose cross-links to aerie=network / ambientops=machine; seams are edge sinks), RelationType::RefersTo, and `estate`/`metadata` on Repo. New `reposystem import manifest` bridges repos.toml (289 unique repos + 2 seams) into the GraphStore — previously the visualisation rendered nothing (web/export.json was an empty stub). New unified `export --format estate-json` envelope (schema reposystem/estate-export@1) is consumed by the web HUD (added estate selector + dashed external-seam rendering); DOT export renders seams too. Nickel contracts (config/{contracts,reposystem}.ncl) aligned to the Rust taxonomy; config/tools.ncl "super power collection" registry added; spec/DATA-MODEL.adoc made normative; GRAPH-STRUCTURE.md marked superseded. Build fix: gix `sha1` feature (gix-hash Kind::Sha1 was cfg'd out -> pre-existing compile break on rustc 1.94). Fresh suite 113/113. Consolidation gitlink surgery (orphan avatar-fabrication-facility/claim-forge, rpa-elysium path conflict) deferred to a follow-up PR.
- 2026-06-02: Phase-2 standalone-vs-local verification — the 7 sub-projects (dirs with both .machine_readable/ + .github/) checked vs ground truth (git ls-tree, .gitmodules, GitHub search index). Only rpa-elysium is a real standalone repo (its gitlink is broken — declared a submodule but committed as a tree); the other 6 (bitfuckit, contractiles, gui, recon-silly-ation, scaffoldia, stateful-artefacts) are local-only. Orphan gitlinks avatar-fabrication-facility + claim-forge (no .gitmodules URL, no forge repo) surfaced. Doc: docs/PHASE-2-STANDALONE-VS-LOCAL-VERIFICATION-2026-06-02.adoc; ECOSYSTEM-STATUS.adoc two "Unknown" rows corrected. PR #91.
- 2026-06-02: Governance CI baseline — the estate banned_language_file gate now bans ReScript (.res). Added .hypatia-ignore baselining the 213 pre-existing .res files (new .res still flagged) and exempting the 22 ATS2 files as an ALLOWED language (the central enforce list over-reaches; tracked #94). AffineScript toolchain built locally; res-to-affine --partial over the 75 first-party .res emitted 0/75 compilable ports (397 TODO holes) — confirming the ReScript→AffineScript port is human work (epic #93; WIP skeletons #92). All 15 PR-#91 checks green.
- 2026-05-18: repo-batcher #56 from-scratch build-out — L1–L4 ATS2 core (just tc-ats2=0), L5 self-contained C archive (ATS_DYNLOADFLAG 0 link fix, just ats2-lib=0), L6 Idris2 typed ABI w/ machine-checked theorems (just abi-check=0), L7 patscc-linked Zig CLI binding the genuine ATS2 C ABI, L8 fixture-backed just e2e=0. Independently fiction-reviewed from a clean clone. PR #59 merged (4c2d29f); issue #56 CLOSED-COMPLETED.
- 2026-05-18: docs-truth — README/IMPLEMENTATION-STATUS/ARCHITECTURE corrected from the inverse anti-fiction defect ("still a stub") to the verified L1–L8 reality (PR #61). "No V ever" retained as true history.
- 2026-05-18: Estate-aggregator organization landed (PR #63, branch feat/estate-aggregator-organization)
- repos.toml (generated, 297 repos) + repos.groups.toml (hand-maintained epic index)
- scripts/{gen-repos-manifest,thread,sync-aggregator,fix-stale-submodule-urls}.sh
- Justfile: repos-manifest/thread/sync-aggregator/aggregator-drift recipes + fixed
